OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778054737
OL,3,CIran's attempts to stir up violence in
OL,4,CUK 'will not be tolerated,' says
OL,5,CStarmer
OL,7,FThe prime minister has warned there
OL,8,Fwill be "consequences" if foreign
OL,9,Factors are found to be behind the
OL,10,Frecent spate of antisemitic attacks in
OL,11,Fthe UK.
OL,13,FAddressing government ministers,
OL,14,Fpolice chiefs, and community leaders
OL,15,Fin Downing Street, Sir Keir Starmer
OL,16,Fconfirmed officials were investigating
OL,17,Fwhether foreign states were
OL,18,Fresponsible for stirring up the hatred
OL,19,Fbehind attacks like Golders Green.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
