PN,30902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778054737
OL,3,CIran's attempts to stir up violence in
OL,4,CUK 'will not be tolerated,' says
OL,5,CStarmer
OL,7,F"Our message to Iran or to any other
OL,8,Fcountry that might seek to promote
OL,9,Fviolence, hatred or division in
OL,10,Fsociety is that it will not be
OL,11,Ftolerated," Starmer said.
OL,13,F"We are clear that these actions will
OL,14,Fhave consequences if that proves to be
OL,15,Fthe case."
OL,17,FThe prime minister also announced a
OL,18,Fseries of measures and additional
OL,19,Ffunding to tackle rising antisemitism
OL,20,Fafter a series of recent attacks and
OL,21,Farsons targeting the Jewish community.
