OL,3,CIran's attempts to stir up violence in
OL,4,CUK 'will not be tolerated,' says
OL,5,CStarmer
OL,7,FAmong these are new expectations for
OL,8,Funiversities and arts bodies, as well
OL,9,Fas additional funding to support
OL,10,Fcommunity safety projects.
OL,12,FLast week's stabbing in Golders Green
OL,13,Fwas the latest in a series of attacks
OL,14,Fon Britain's Jewish community, which
OL,15,Fhave contributed to concerns that
OL,16,Fantisemitism is on the rise.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
