OL,3,CIran's attempts to stir up violence in
OL,4,CUK 'will not be tolerated,' says
OL,5,CStarmer
OL,7,FDescribing the situation as a "crisis"
OL,8,Fin the wake of the Golders Green
OL,9,Fattack, Starmer said new legislation
OL,10,Fwould be rushed through to tackle
OL,11,F"malign threats".
OL,13,FThe government has promised a new law
OL,14,Fto allow it to take action against
OL,15,Fstate-backed groups amid calls for the
OL,16,Fproscription of Iran's Islamic
OL,17,FRevolutionary Guard Corps (IRGC).
