OL,3,CIran's attempts to stir up violence in
OL,4,CUK 'will not be tolerated,' says
OL,5,CStarmer
OL,7,FAt a roundtable of senior figures from
OL,8,Fthe police, representatives from the
OL,9,Farts, higher education, trade unions
OL,10,Fand businesses, Starmer also promised
OL,11,Fnew action to implement a "zero
OL,12,Ftolerance" approach to antisemitism on
OL,13,Funiversity campuses and action in the
OL,14,Farts.
OL,16,FUniversities will now be expected to
OL,17,F"demonstrate action" to tackle
OL,18,Fantisemitism among students, the PM
OL,19,Fsaid.
OL,26,@sD@[OUtD@JO]yD@AOUyD@TO]
