OL,3,CIran's attempts to stir up violence in
OL,4,CUK 'will not be tolerated,' says
OL,5,CStarmer
OL,7,F"We will now expect them to publish
OL,8,Fthe scale of the problem on their
OL,9,Fcampuses, as well as the specific
OL,10,Fsteps they have taken to clamp down on
OL,11,Fit. There will be zero tolerance for
OL,12,Finaction," he added.
OL,14,FThe Arts Council will be expected to
OL,15,Fwithdraw funding and claw it back from
OL,16,Fanyone who is found to promote
OL,17,Fantisemitism.
