OL,3,CIran's attempts to stir up violence in
OL,4,CUK 'will not be tolerated,' says
OL,5,CStarmer
OL,7,FThis is on top of the additional #25
OL,8,Fmillion funding increase for security
OL,9,Fannounced in the immediate wake of the
OL,10,FGolders Green, bringing the total
OL,11,Ffunding of Jewish community security
OL,12,Fprimarily in London and Manchester to
OL,13,F#58 million this year.
OL,15,FShortly before Starmer's announcement,
OL,16,Fthe Metropolitan Police announced that
OL,17,Fcounter-terror police are
OL,18,Finvestigating an arson at a former
OL,19,Fsynagogue in Tower Hamlets, east
OL,20,FLondon.
