OL,3,CIran's attempts to stir up violence in
OL,4,CUK 'will not be tolerated,' says
OL,5,CStarmer
OL,7,FThis follows similar arson attacks on
OL,8,Fa Golders Green memorial wall, two
OL,9,FHatzolah ambulances, and an attack on
OL,10,FManchester's Heaton Park synagogue
OL,11,Flast year, which left two people dead.
OL,13,FThe prime minister's warning to Iran
OL,14,Fcomes after the Iranian ambassador was
OL,15,Fsummoned by the Foreign Office over
OL,16,Fincendiary posts made by the Iranian
OL,17,Fembassy on Telegram.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
