OL,3,CIran's attempts to stir up violence in
OL,4,CUK 'will not be tolerated,' says
OL,5,CStarmer
OL,7,FThe post, which included the line:
OL,8,F"Let us all surrender to killing
OL,9,Frather than handing over the country
OL,10,Fto the enemy," purported to be
OL,11,Frecruiting for the "Sacrifice for the
OL,12,FHomeland Campaign".
OL,14,FThe FCDO said in a statement at the
OL,15,Ftime: "The Minister for the Middle
OL,16,FEast, Hamish Falconer, summoned the
OL,17,FAmbassador of the Islamic Republic of
OL,18,FIran to the United Kingdom, in
OL,19,Fresponse to the Iranian embassy's
OL,20,Funacceptable and inflammatory comments
OL,21,Fon social media.
