OL,3,CIran's attempts to stir up violence in
OL,4,CUK 'will not be tolerated,' says
OL,5,CStarmer
OL,7,F"The Minister made clear that these
OL,8,Factions and comments were completely
OL,9,Funacceptable, and that the Embassy
OL,10,Fmust cease any form of communications
OL,11,Fthat could be interpreted as
OL,12,Fencouraging violence in the UK or
OL,13,Finternationally."
OL,15,FA spokesperson for the Iranian Embassy
OL,16,Fsaid via a statement: "Iranians around
OL,17,Fthe world have always cared deeply
OL,18,Fabout their homeland and the
OL,19,Fprotection of its territorial
OL,20,Fintegrity, and they always will.
