OL,7,F"The 'Jan Fada' platform is intended
OL,8,Ffor all Iranians who wish to support
OL,9,Fand defend their country, and it does
OL,10,Fnot promote any form of hostility.
OL,12,F"Any claims or assumptions to the
OL,13,Fcontrary are simply unfounded. Such
OL,14,Fbiased judgments are made hastily and
OL,15,Fwithout proper understanding."
